                <p><b>Cook Time:</b> 25 minutes</p>
                <p><b>Servings:</b> ?? <p>
            </div> 

            <div id="preparation">
                <h2>Preparation</h2>
                <h3>Equipment</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Stove</li>
                    <li>Large pot</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Ingredients</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Group 1</li>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Vegetable broth, 6 cups</li>
                        <li>Dry green Lentils, 1 cup</li>
                        <li>Millet, 1/4 cup</li>
                        <li>Onion, diced, 1 medium</li>
                        <li>Celery, 1 stalk diced </li>
                        <li>Carrot, 1 peeled and diced</li>
                        <li>Garlic, 4 cloves minced</li>
                        <li>Coriander, 2 tsp</li>
                        <li>Cumin, 2 tsp</li>
                        <li>Tumeric, 1/2 tsp</li>
                        <li>Sage, 1/4 tsp</li>
                    </ul>
                    <li>Group 2</li>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Yellow miso paste, 1 Tbsp</li>
                        <li>Collard greens, 7-8 pieces sliced</li>
                        <li>Salt, 1 tsp</li>
                    </ul>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="cooking">
                <h2>Cooking</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Add all Group 1 ingredients to the pot, bring to a boil</li>
                    <li>Reduce to simmer for 20 minutes</li>
                    <li>Add all Group 2 ingredients, stir</li>
                    <li>Let simmer for 5 more minutes</li>
                    
                </ol>

            </div>

            <div id="notes">
                <h2>Notes & Tips</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Yum</li>
                    
                </ul>

            </div>

